deal.product_description: Bellroy leather phone case made specifically for the Google Pixel 8, constructed from premium Leather Working Group–rated leather with aluminum buttons for durability. The case offers a slim profile with a soft-lined interior to protect the phone, maintains wireless charging compatibility, and provides refined leather craftsmanship and edge protection while preserving phone functionality.

Roborock Qrevo Series QV 35S robot vacuum and mop with 10,000Pa suction, smart navigation and app control. The unit features a self‑emptying base, dynamic mopping, a dual anti‑tangle system to handle hair and debris, and onboard mapping for efficient room coverage. Model: QV 35S.

Open-box Samsung LS49CG95ENXZA 49" curved ultrawide gaming monitor offers a 5120×1440 dual‑QHD resolution, a 240Hz refresh rate, and 1ms response time for very smooth gaming visuals. It supports AMD FreeSync Premium Pro, includes USB 3.0 ports, and its large curved panel is aimed at immersive sim‑racing and multitasking setups that benefit from extra horizontal screen real estate.
